h3cVoiceGKClient.name: h3cVoiceGKClient

revisions.description: The initial version of this MIB file.

h3cVoiceGKClient.contactinfo: PLAT Team Huawei 3Com Technologies co.,Ltd. Shang-Di Information Industry Base, Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.huawei-3com.com Zip:100085
h3cVoiceGKClient.description: This MIB file is to provide the the definition of GK client configuration.

h3cVoRasOn.name: h3cVoRasOn
h3cVoRasOn.description: This object indicates whether the GK(Gate Keeper) client function of this gateaway is enabled. The value couldn't be set to enable unless h3cVoH323GWID, h3cVoGwIPAddress, h3cVoH323GKIPAddress, and h3cVoH323GKID has been set.

h3cVoGwIPAddressType.name: h3cVoGwIPAddressType
h3cVoGwIPAddressType.description: This object indicates the IP address type of the the interface through which the gateway is connected to the GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoGwIPAddress.name: h3cVoGwIPAddress
h3cVoGwIPAddress.description: This object indicates the IP address of the interface through which the gateway is connected to the GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GWID.name: h3cVoH323GWID
h3cVoH323GWID.description: This object indicates the ID of this H323 gateway. The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GKID.name: h3cVoH323GKID
h3cVoH323GKID.description: This object indicates the ID of the GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GKIPAddressType.name: h3cVoH323GKIPAddressType
h3cVoH323GKIPAddressType.description: This object indicates the IP address of the GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GKIPAddress.name: h3cVoH323GKIPAddress
h3cVoH323GKIPAddress.description: This object indicates the IP address of the GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GKPort.name: h3cVoH323GKPort
h3cVoH323GKPort.description: This object indicates the RAS port of GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GK2ID.name: h3cVoH323GK2ID
h3cVoH323GK2ID.description: This object indicates the ID of the slave GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GK2IPAddressType.name: h3cVoH323GK2IPAddressType
h3cVoH323GK2IPAddressType.description: This object indicates the IP address of the slave GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GK2IPAddress.name: h3cVoH323GK2IPAddress
h3cVoH323GK2IPAddress.description: This object indicates the IP address of the slave GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GK2Port.name: h3cVoH323GK2Port
h3cVoH323GK2Port.description: This object indicates the RAS communication port of slave GK(Gate Keeper). The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GKSecurityCall.name: h3cVoH323GKSecurityCall
h3cVoH323GKSecurityCall.description: This object indicates whether security call is enabled. The value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.

h3cVoH323GKSecurityPWDType.name: h3cVoH323GKSecurityPWDType
h3cVoH323GKSecurityPWDType.description: This object indicates the type of security call password.

h3cVoH323GKSecurityPWD.name: h3cVoH323GKSecurityPWD
h3cVoH323GKSecurityPWD.description: This object indicates the security call password. This value couldn't be modified unless h3cVoRasOn is 'disable'.
